{"tid":1591790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[再開]有冇學生巴絲發夢發到冇錢，想教小學功課輔導賺下零用","createTime":"2019-09-24T10:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T06:54:08.000Z","uid":198801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe817b6110c30e52e452b10ad0fdc913b32702be","tid":1591790,"uid":198801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:00:45.000Z","msg":"小弟幾年前大學畢業開左間屋邨補習社，<br />\n如果有中學大學巴絲發夢發到冇錢，<br />\n或者藍絲屋企人唔比零用，<br />\n但又唔想問其他人足借錢，<br />\n歡迎放學後黎我間補習社幫下手，自力更新賺少少零用<br />\n地點：觀塘區<br />\n人工：60-70/hr, 成本所限幫唔到太多，可以請到兩三位手足<br />\n時間：星期一至五 4:00-8:00左右，唔一定番足5日<br />\n有意留TG，唔洗話我知你點發夢，保障自己保障他人"},{"pid":"83617634fe1c722f4040b416e431087ac2d5f412","tid":1591790,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"8fc22c936f4097c4473c66dbdc89ea37fcf5e6e9","tid":1591790,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"support,社區互助機制"},{"pid":"20ef8baedd964f36cfaa068351c01fadaf1f9ab5","tid":1591790,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"457f06955e4791a74d04f30868498cb8c9b7efda","tid":1591790,"uid":198801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"dfc8d54df76534c8f7234a5f0867a8fe60d475c2","tid":1591790,"uid":310348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T10:35:34.000Z","msg":"而家成副身家得今年垃圾政府啱啱派嗰4000蚊算唔算冇錢<br />\n利申:黨大學渣"},{"pid":"c18892cdb89ed98424fee4b62bb6d11010af3d3e","tid":1591790,"uid":198801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc8d54df76534c8f7234a5f0867a8fe60d475c2","tid":1591790,"uid":3